{"tid":2092110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本自民黨擬 1. 向港人提供工作簽證 2. 譴責中國 3. 取消習近平訪日","createTime":"2020-07-03T04:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T09:34:08.000Z","uid":13663,"like":215,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"3514a7b9282505e13669a617ffe2e50bd035f83d","tid":2092110,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"港區國安法：日本自民黨擬提決議 考慮向港人提供工作簽證<br />\n1 小時前<br />\n<br />\n北京在香港推行《港區國安法》引起國際反彈，日媒日本放送協會（NHK）周五（3日）報道，日本執政自民黨將於日內向政府提交決議，要求譴責中國。決議又呼籲，政府應考慮向有意離港的港人提供工作簽證。"},{"pid":"92775f9d5c0d50a856d06f55c4c7c19d5b3a492b","tid":2092110,"uid":155818,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:59:16.000Z","msg":"取消習近平訪日最有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4d9c525497d48a1f4ec3332811678baade0d17","tid":2092110,"uid":13663,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"中國政府強推《港區國安法》，引發國際社會強列反彈。據日本NHK報導，日本執政的自由民主黨（簡稱自民黨）正採取行動，取消日本政府邀請中國國家主席習近平訪日的計畫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200703/ZVQZX2Z5WW3KG6B2KMOJEGWZ2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200703%2FZVQZX2Z5WW3KG6B2KMOJEGWZ2Y%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=8aacfbbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200703%2FZVQZX2Z5WW3KG6B2KMOJEGWZ2Y%2F&h=96343a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200703/ZVQZX2Z5WW3KG6B2KMOJEGWZ2Y/</a>"},{"pid":"0b24b4764a1101a42ef6ce8c8bab7ca5a739c6da","tid":2092110,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fcb6f5c198340a39e1bb5f3d4f3bb477e9daf8","tid":2092110,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":